Project Title:
    Paycheck Budgeting Utility

Project Description:
    This utility's purpose is to automate my paycheck budgeting. The user will be prompted to enter their paycheck amount and prompted to go through a configuration of their budget if its their first time using the utility. 
    Configuration includes setting up sectors for their budget and if needed adding specific sub-sectors inside the sectors. Afterwards, the configuration will be saved for future use. After this process is complete, the utility
    will automatically budget your paycheck and output into a formatted excel file.

Scope of Work:
    Saving user configuration:
        Function to serialize user configuration.
        Function to deserialize user configuration.
    
    Output to Excel:
        Function to output formatted budget into an excel file.

    Budgeting:
        Function to create sectors of the budget (Stage 1).
        Function to create sub-sectors inside sectors (Stage 2).

    Interface:
        Create a command menu using Typer Library.
        Create a command to budget a paycheck.
        Create a command to configure a budget.

Due Date:
    January 12th 2025

        

